        "Person",
        "REPORT"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。所以起点是一个Person节点，然后连接到REPORT？这个REPORT具体代表什么模块？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Person",
        "REPORT"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "REPORT是诊断报告提交入口，对应HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine。患者提交后，系统要先做CAPTCHA验证，防止机器人滥用。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "REPORT",
        "CAPTCHA"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我画出了Person到REPORT，再到CAPTCHA判断节点的流程。CAPTCHA有两个分支对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CAPTCHA"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，验证失败直接进TRASH，也就是HealthTech_LabAnalyzer的废弃队列。验证通过才进入AUTO_CLASSIFIER。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CAPTCHA",
        "TRASH",
        "AUTO_CLASSIFIER"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加CAPTCHA到TRASH的NO分支，以及到AUTO_CLASSIFIER的YES分支。AUTO_CLASSIFIER是自动分类器？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "AUTO_CLASSIFIER"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "没错，AUTO_CLASSIFIER对应HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault，负责判断报告是否需要人工复核。如果分类器判断为NO，直接通知用户未通过，走NOTIFY_NO。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "AUTO_CLASSIFIER",
        "NOTIFY_NO"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，AUTO_CLASSIFIER的NO分支指向NOTIFY_NO。那YES分支呢？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "AUTO_CLASSIFIER",
        "NOTIFY_NO"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "YES分支进入C_CROWD，这是我们的众包复核节点，对应HealthTech_EMR_Sync。需要人工专家二次确认。",
