      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，C_CROWD判断为YES时，说明诊断确认无误，走NOTIFY_YES通知患者，对应HealthTech_PatientRecords。",
